    <div class="main review-item" id="6162933">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6162933/" class="title-link">《贫穷的本质》读书笔记</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6162933"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/iamsujie/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2355899-6.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/iamsujie/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">iamsujie</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-07-15"
      class="main-meta">2013-07-15 12:39:02</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6162933_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  一直以来，深感自己有很多思维方式是“穷人”的，并不是说好、或者不好，而是，没搞清这些思维的原因，可能会阻碍自己做出更好的选择。所以，前段时间弄了一本《贫穷的本质》看，有些收获，简记如下，提一句，书里对贫穷的定义是每天收入小于0.99美元的人群，全球有10亿，这是...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/6162933/#comments">(10回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">78有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6162933_full" class="hidden">
